{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/04\/allah-answers-dua-yunus\/","url_meta":{"origin":18564,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Yunus: Allah answers supplication of Prophet Jonah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplication of Jonah, Dhul Nun, when he called upon Allah inside the belly of the whale was this, 'There is no God but You, glory be to You for I have certainly been among the wrongdoers,'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":640,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/19\/be-determined-in-your-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":18564,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Be determined, certain in your supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cWhen one of you calls upon Allah, let him be determined in the supplication and he should not say, 'O Allah, give me if You will,' for there is no one to coerce Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12007,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/04\/beat-dhikr-dua-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18564,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Best remembrance, best supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best\u00a0remembrance is to declare there is no God but Allah. The best\u00a0supplication is to declare all praise is due to Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3383 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/13\/dua-ease-answer-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":18564,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplicate in prosperity if you want answer in adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like for Allah to answer him during times of hardship and difficulty, let him supplicate often during times of ease.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3382 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0